606
00:46:41,686 --> 00:46:43,021
Ah...

607
00:46:43,523 --> 00:46:49,175
Because Professor Kim Woo Chul got
hired after Choi Kyu Won was dismissed?

608
00:46:49,206 --> 00:46:51,566
