708
00:55:28,710 --> 00:55:31,271
- It's me, Ha No Ra.
- Ha No Ra?

709
00:55:38,625 --> 00:55:41,362
What brings you here
so early in the morning?

710
00:55:42,753 --> 00:55:44,943
I wanted to say thank you.

711
00:55:45,679 --> 00:55:46,869
